    "If today was a plant, draw how many leaves it grew (or lost) today." : {
      "comment" : "A prompt that asks the user to draw how many leaves a plant has grown or lost today.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Si aujourd'hui était une plante, dessinez combien de feuilles elle a poussé (ou perdu) aujourd'hui."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "もし今日が植物だったら、今日のうちに増えた（または減った）葉っぱの数を描いてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "오늘이 식물이라면, 오늘 잎이 얼마나 자랐는지(또는 떨어졌는지) 그려보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果今天是一株植物，画出它今天长出（或掉落）了多少片叶子。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your brain was a weather map, draw the clouds or sun over it now." : {
      "comment" : "A doodling prompt that asks the user to draw a weather map with clouds or a sun.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Si votre cerveau était une carte météo, dessinez les nuages ou le soleil dessus maintenant."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "もしあなたの脳が天気図だったら、今そこにある雲や太陽を描いてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "당신의 머릿속이 날씨 지도라면, 지금 그 위에 구름이나 해를 그려보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果你的大脑是一张天气图，画出现在上面的云彩或太阳。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your focus was a flashlight beam, draw what it is pointing at." : {
      "comment" : "A doodling prompt that asks the user to draw what a flashlight beam is pointing at.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Si votre concentration était un faisceau de lampe torche, dessinez ce qu'il éclaire."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "もし集中が懐中電灯の光だったら、それが何を照らしているかを描いてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "집중력이 손전등 빛이라면, 지금 무엇을 비추고 있는지 그려보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果你的注意力是一束手电筒光，画出它正照向什么。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your stress was a jar of tangled wires, draw how messy the wires are." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Si votre stress était un bocal de fils emmêlés, dessinez à quel point les fils sont en désordre."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "もしストレスが絡まったワイヤーの瓶だったら、ワイヤーがどれだけぐちゃぐちゃかを描いてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "스트레스가 엉킨 전선이 담긴 병이라면, 전선이 얼마나 복잡한지 그려보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果你的压力是一罐缠在一起的电线，画出这些电线有多乱。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Imagine seeing a year of your life in a single glance. Each Joodle carries a special piece of memory. Always private. Always yours." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the feature that allows users to see all their past Joodles in one place.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Imaginez voir une année de votre vie en un seul coup d'œil. Chaque Joodle porte un fragment de souvenir. Toujours privé. Toujours à vous."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "自分の人生1年分を一目で見渡すところを想像してください。各 Joodle には大切な記憶のかけらが宿っています。常にプライベート。常にあなたのもの。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "인생의 1년을 한눈에 본다고 상상해 보세요. 각 Joodle에는 특별한 기억의 조각이 담겨 있습니다. 언제나 비공개. 언제나 당신의 것."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "想象一眼纵览你一整年的生活。每个涂鸦承载着一段特别的记忆。始终私密。始终属于你。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
