    "Switching between subscription plans is handled by the App Store. Tap a new plan to purchase it, or use \"Manage or Cancel via App Store\" to change or cancel your current subscription." : {
      "comment" : "A disclaimer explaining that switching between subscription plans is managed by the App Store, and that users can manage or cancel their subscriptions through the App Store.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le changement d'offre d'abonnement est géré par l'App Store. Touchez une nouvelle offre pour l'acheter, ou utilisez \"Gérer ou annuler via l'App Store\" pour modifier ou annuler votre abonnement actuel."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "サブスクリプションプランの切り替えは App Store で行われます。新しいプランをタップして購入するか、「App Store で管理または解約」を使って現在のサブスクリプションを変更または解約してください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "구독 요금제 전환은 App Store에서 처리됩니다. 새 요금제를 탭해 구매하거나 \"App Store를 통해 관리 또는 취소\"를 사용해 현재 구독을 변경하거나 취소하세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "订阅方案切换由 App Store 处理。点击新方案即可购买，或使用\"通过 App Store 管理或取消\"来变更或取消当前订阅。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
